status: passed
summary: Jeff approved resetting data when appropriate. Operational/demo data was reset while preserving schema, buildings, users/admin users, role/config/login tables. Seeded one clean E2E example per core functionality before future real data load.
reset_scope:
  preserved:
    - public.users
    - public.admin_users
    - public.admin_role_assignments
    - public.buildings
    - public.building_module_config
    - schema/functions/RLS/config/code
  reset_operational_tables_include:
    - pqrs_cases / pqrs_status_history
    - inspection_plans / points / rounds / results / findings
    - incident_tickets / incident_activity_log
    - work_assignments
    - inventory_locations / items / movements
    - documents
    - service_listings
    - weekly_reports
    - spend_policies
    - purchase/compliance/audit/session/import/staff/role operational tables
seed_examples:
  pqrs: VV-PQRS-E2E-000001
  recorrido: E2E-RECORRIDO / REC-E2E-001 / seed finding
  work_assignment: WO-E2E-001
  incident: INC-E2E-001
  inventory: E2E-CLORO at E2E-ALM with balance 3/reorder 5
  provider: Proveedor E2E Jardinería
  document: E2E Reglamento de prueba
  weekly_report: Semana E2E
  spend_policy: seed-spend-policy-e2e
verification:
  - counts verified exactly one row in each seeded operational table
  - public.lookup_pqrs_case('VV-PQRS-E2E-000001') returned exactly one row
  - public.get_md04_lite_exceptions(VV building) returned seeded OPEN_FINDING and STOCK_OUT exceptions
  - node scripts/production-smoke.mjs passed
  - node scripts/pqrs-rpc-smoke.mjs --live --known-ref VV-PQRS-E2E-000001 passed
  - node scripts/recorridos-md04-preflight.mjs --live passed
remaining:
  - Jeff reviews one E2E example per functionality
  - after approval, perform real data load/backfill from private exports/sources
